# AI Says PRD

## Overview
AI Says is an AI-powered chatbot that provides stock analysis and trading strategies for Chinese retail investors. The chatbot utilizes AI algorithms to analyze financial reports, key stock indicators, and market trends to offer personalized recommendations and trading strategies. The goal is to empower Chinese retail investors by providing them with accurate and actionable insights to make informed investment decisions.

## Target Customers
The primary target customers for AI Says are retail investors from China. These investors may have limited knowledge and experience in stock analysis and trading strategies. AI Says aims to bridge this knowledge gap and provide a user-friendly platform for investors to access AI-driven stock analysis and trading strategies.

## Business Objective Opportunity
The business objective of AI Says is to empower Chinese retail investors by providing AI-driven stock analysis and trading strategies. The opportunity lies in the growing demand for AI-powered investment tools in the Chinese market. By offering a comprehensive and user-friendly platform, AI Says aims to capture a significant market share and establish itself as a trusted and reliable source of investment insights.

The success of AI Says will be measured by metrics such as user engagement, user satisfaction, and the number of successful trades made by users based on the provided recommendations. Additionally, customer complaints and negative feedback will be monitored to identify areas for improvement and address any downsides.

## Scope/Out-of-Scope
The scope of AI Says includes the following features:
- AI analysis of stocks' financial reports
- AI analysis of key stock indicators
- AI assistance in strategy implementation and backtesting
- User-friendly chat interface
- Comprehensive stock database

The out-of-scope items for AI Says include:
- Providing real-time stock prices and trading capabilities
- Offering financial advice or personalized investment recommendations
- Providing access to international stock markets

AI Says will be considered "done" when it successfully provides accurate and timely stock analysis, offers a user-friendly chat interface, and assists users in implementing and backtesting trading strategies.

