## Additional Requirements and Feature Details
The key features of AI Says are as follows:

### AI Analysis of Stocks' Financial Reports
- Analyzes financial statements, balance sheets, and income statements to provide insights on a company's financial health.
- Identifies trends, patterns, and anomalies in financial data to help investors make informed decisions.
- Provides recommendations based on financial analysis.

### AI Analysis of Key Stock Indicators
- Evaluates key financial ratios such as Return on Equity (ROE) and Price-to-Earnings (P/E) ratio to assess a company's profitability and valuation.
- Compares these indicators with industry benchmarks to identify potential investment opportunities.
- Generates reports and visualizations to present the analysis in an easy-to-understand format.

### AI Assistance in Strategy Implementation and Backtesting
- Provides trading strategies based on technical analysis, market trends, and historical data.
- Helps investors implement trading strategies by providing real-time alerts and notifications.
- Offers backtesting capabilities to evaluate the performance of trading strategies using historical data.

### User-Friendly Chat Interface
- Allows users to interact with the AI through a chat interface, making it easy to ask questions and receive real-time responses.
- Supports natural language processing to understand user queries and provide relevant information.
- Offers personalized recommendations based on user preferences and investment goals.

### Comprehensive Stock Database
- Includes a vast database of Chinese stocks, covering a wide range of industries and market segments.
- Regularly updates stock data to ensure accurate and up-to-date information for analysis.
- Provides detailed company profiles, historical stock prices, and other relevant data for comprehensive analysis.

## Features Release Table
| Features                           | Description   | Accept Criteria | Priority |
|------------------------------------|---------------|-----------------|----------|
| AI Analysis of Stocks' Financial Reports   | AI analyzes financial reports to provide insights on a company's financial health. | Financial analysis accurately identifies trends and anomalies. | High |
| AI Analysis of Key Stock Indicators   | AI evaluates key stock indicators to assess a company's profitability and valuation. | Analysis is based on accurate data and provides actionable insights. | High |
| AI Assistance in Strategy Implementation and Backtesting   | AI provides trading strategies and backtesting capabilities. | Strategies are based on accurate analysis and backtesting results are reliable. | High |
| User-Friendly Chat Interface   | AI interacts with users through a chat interface. | Chat interface is intuitive and provides real-time responses. | Medium |
| Comprehensive Stock Database   | AI has access to a comprehensive stock database. | Database includes a wide range of Chinese stocks with accurate and up-to-date information. | Medium |

## Launch Milestones & Phases
| Timing             | Features/User Stories         | Key Objectives                            |
|--------------------|-------------------------------|-------------------------------------------|
| 08.2023 | Development phase begins | AI model training and database setup |
| 09.2023 | Alpha release | AI analysis of 300 Chinese stocks based on financial reports and key indicators |
| 12.2023 | Beta release | AI analysis of 5000 Chinese stocks, trading strategies, and backtesting capabilities |
| 2024 Q1 | Official release | Comprehensive set of features, including advanced trading strategies, personalized recommendations, and a user-friendly chat interface |